<template>
  <input :value="value" @input="$emit('input', $event.target.value)" />
</template>
<script>
export default {
  name: "MisaInput",
  props: ["value"],
  methods: {},

  data() {
    return {
      firstName: "",
      lastName: "",
      firstNameLabel: "First Name",
      lastNameLabel: "Last Name",
    };
  },
  computed: {
    computedFirstName: {
      get() {
        return this.firstName;
      },
      set(value) {
        this.firstName = value;
      },
    },
    computedLastName: {
      get() {
        return this.lastName;
      },
      set(value) {
        this.lastName = value;
      },
    },
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
